---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Hero from '../components/Hero.astro';
---

<Layout title="Executive Negotiation Coaching - Ahmed K. Hafsi">
  <div class="w-full max-w-6xl mx-auto mt-8 md:mt-16 px-4 md:px-6 relative">
    <!-- Service Introduction with Origin Story -->
    <div class="text-center mb-12 md:mb-16">
      <h1 class="text-3xl md:text-5xl font-serif font-semibold text-white mb-6 relative inline-block">
        <span class="relative z-10">Unlock Your True Value as a Senior Executive</span>
        <span class="absolute -bottom-2 left-0 w-full h-1 bg-accent opacity-70"></span>
      </h1>
      <p class="text-gray-300 max-w-3xl mx-auto text-base md:text-lg mt-6">
        As a negotiation expert with global experience, I've helped C-suite executives, directors, VPs, and Board Members across Asia Pacific, North America and Europe secure millions more in compensation by mastering high-stakes negotiations. My journey began helping friends navigate critical career talks, evolving into a proven system that empowers leaders like you to maximize your worth.
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- Pain Points Section (Condensed) -->
    <div class="w-full mb-12 md:mb-16">
      <div class="text-center mb-8">
        <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-serif text-white mb-4">Challenges You Face</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-300 max-w-2xl mx-auto">Negotiating as a senior executive is complex. Here's what might be holding you back:</p>
      </div>
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
        <!-- Pain Point 1 -->
        <div class="relative group bg-card backdrop-blur-sm border border-gray-800 p-6 rounded-xl flex flex-col min-h-[250px]">
          <div class="mb-4 text-accent">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-10 w-10" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M12 6V4m0 2a2 2 0 100 4m0-4a2 2 0 110 4m-6 8a2 2 0 100-4m0 4a2 2 0 110-4m0 4v2m0-6V4m6 6v10m6-2a2 2 0 100-4m0 4a2 2 0 110-4m0 4v2m0-6V4" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-serif text-white mb-3">Overwhelmed by Offer Complexity?</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-300 text-sm flex-grow">
            High-level offers involve many moving parts beyond just salary, making it hard to assess the full picture and negotiate effectively.
          </p>
        </div>
        <!-- Pain Point 2 -->
        <div class="relative group bg-card backdrop-blur-sm border border-gray-800 p-6 rounded-xl flex flex-col min-h-[250px]">
          <div class="mb-4 text-accent">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-10 w-10" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M8 7h12m0 0l-4-4m4 4l-4 4m0 6H4m0 0l4 4m-4-4l4-4" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-serif text-white mb-3">Struggling with Board/Exec Talks?</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-300 text-sm flex-grow">
            Facing compensation committees, senior leadership, or navigating board dynamics feels like a maze of politics and scrutiny.
          </p>
        </div>
        <!-- Pain Point 3 - Updated -->
        <div class="relative group bg-card backdrop-blur-sm border border-gray-800 p-6 rounded-xl flex flex-col min-h-[250px]">
          <div class="mb-4 text-accent">
             <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-10 w-10" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M8.228 9c.549-1.165 2.03-2 3.772-2 2.21 0 4 1.343 4 3 0 1.4-1.278 2.575-3.006 2.907-.542.104-.994.54-.994 1.093m0 3h.01M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-serif text-white mb-3">Feeling Unprepared for Key Talks?</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-300 text-sm flex-grow">
            Entering crucial salary or promotion negotiations without a clear strategy or confidence can cost you significantly.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Services Section -->
    <div class="text-center mb-12 md:mb-16">
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-serif font-semibold text-white mb-6 relative inline-block">
        <span class="relative z-10">How I Can Help</span>
        <span class="absolute -bottom-2 left-0 w-full h-1 bg-accent opacity-70"></span>
      </h2>
      <p class="text-gray-300 max-w-3xl mx-auto text-base md:text-lg">
        My coaching transforms complex negotiations into opportunities, using proven tactics from behavioral economics and real-world experience across industries like electronics, semiconductors, automotive Tier 1, global consumer tech, chemicals, and pharma.
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 mb-16">
      <!-- Service Card 1 - Updated -->
      <div class="bg-card p-6 rounded-xl border border-gray-700 hover:shadow-accent/20 transition-all duration-300 flex flex-col group relative">
        <h3 class="text-xl md:text-2xl font-serif text-white mb-3 group-hover:text-accent">Executive Negotiation Coaching</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-300 text-sm mb-4">
          Personalized strategies for C-suite, senior leaders, and board members to master high-stakes compensation negotiations.
        </p>
        <ul class="space-y-2 text-gray-300 text-sm flex-grow">
          <li class="flex items-start">
            <span class="text-accent mr-2">•</span>
            Develop tailored negotiation strategies for your specific situation.
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start">
            <span class="text-accent mr-2">•</span>
            Prepare and practice for critical conversations (interviews, reviews).
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start">
            <span class="text-accent mr-2">•</span>
            Learn techniques to articulate your value and counter objections effectively.
          </li>
           <li class="flex items-start">
            <span class="text-accent mr-2">•</span>
            Build confidence to navigate difficult negotiation dynamics, including board-level discussions.
          </li>
        </ul>
        <a href="/contact" class="text-accent hover:text-white text-sm mt-4 inline-flex items-center">
          Learn More
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-4 w-4 ml-1" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M14 5l7 7m0 0l-7 7m7-7H3" />
          </svg>
        </a>
      </div>
      <!-- Service Card 2 -->
      <div class="bg-card p-6 rounded-xl border border-gray-700 hover:shadow-accent/20 transition-all duration-300 flex flex-col group relative">
        <h3 class="text-xl md:text-2xl font-serif text-white mb-3 group-hover:text-accent">Negotiation Skills Training</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-300 text-sm mb-4">
          A repeatable framework to boost your earning potential throughout your career.
        </p>
        <ul class="space-y-2 text-gray-300 text-sm flex-grow">
          <li class="flex items-start">
            <span class="text-accent mr-2">•</span>
            Leverage persuasion psychology to influence decisions.
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start">
            <span class="text-accent mr-2">•</span>
            Frame requests for easy employer agreement.
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start">
            <span class="text-accent mr-2">•</span>
            Practice real-world scenarios with feedback.
          </li>
        </ul>
        <a href="/contact" class="text-accent hover:text-white text-sm mt-4 inline-flex items-center">
          Learn More
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-4 w-4 ml-1" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M14 5l7 7m0 0l-7 7m7-7H3" />
          </svg>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Take Control Section (Moved Up) -->
    <div class="relative py-8 md:py-12 bg-card/50 backdrop-blur-sm">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 md:px-8 text-center">
        <h3 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-serif text-white mb-6">Take Control of Your Future</h3>
        <p class="text-lg text-gray-300 mb-8">
          Don't leave money on the table. Strategic negotiation can add hundreds of thousands to your career earnings.
        </p>
        <div class="p-6 bg-card border border-gray-700 rounded-xl">
          <h4 class="text-xl font-serif text-white mb-3">Ready to Start?</h4>
          <p class="text-gray-300 mb-4 text-sm">
            Book a free 20-minute consultation to explore how I can help you secure the compensation you deserve. Spots are limited—act now.
          </p>
          <a
            href="/contact"
            class="w-full sm:w-auto inline-block bg-accent hover:bg-accent/90 text-black font-medium px-8 py-3 rounded-lg transition-all duration-300 hover:shadow-lg hover:shadow-accent/30"
          >
            Book Your Free Consultation
          </a>
          <div class="mt-6 flex flex-col sm:flex-row justify-center gap-4 text-sm text-gray-400">
            <p class="flex items-center">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-4 w-4 mr-1 text-accent" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m5.618-4.016A11.955 11.955 0 0112 2.944a11.955 11.955 0 01-8.618 3.04A12.02 12.02 0 003 9c0 5.591 3.824 10.29 9 11.622 5.176-1.332 9-6.03 9-11.622 0-1.042-.133-2.052-.382-3.016z" />
              </svg>
              100% Confidential
            </p>
            <p class="flex items-center">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-4 w-4 mr-1 text-accent" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
              </svg>
              No Obligation
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- FAQ Section - Updated -->
    <div class="py-8 md:py-12">
      <div class="text-center mb-8">
        <h3 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-serif text-white mb-4">Common Questions</h3>
      </div>
      <div class="space-y-4">
        <details class="group bg-card border border-gray-800 rounded-lg">
          <summary class="flex items-center justify-between p-4 cursor-pointer hover:bg-card/80">
            <h4 class="text-base text-white">How do you ensure confidentiality?</h4>
            <span class="text-accent group-open:rotate-180 transition-transform">+</span>
          </summary>
          <div class="p-4 pt-0 bg-gray-900/40 text-sm text-gray-300">
            Client confidentiality is paramount. All discussions are strictly confidential. We can operate under a Non-Disclosure Agreement (NDA) if preferred, or discuss sensitive details like compensation using ranges and anonymized company information to protect your privacy.
          </div>
        </details>
         <details class="group bg-card border border-gray-800 rounded-lg">
          <summary class="flex items-center justify-between p-4 cursor-pointer hover:bg-card/80">
            <h4 class="text-base text-white">What does the coaching process look like?</h4>
            <span class="text-accent group-open:rotate-180 transition-transform">+</span>
          </summary>
          <div class="p-4 pt-0 bg-gray-900/40 text-sm text-gray-300">
            We start with a consultation to understand your goals and situation. Coaching involves personalized sessions focused on strategy development, role-playing key conversations, and refining your negotiation approach. The process is tailored to your specific needs and timeline.
          </div>
        </details>
         <details class="group bg-card border border-gray-800 rounded-lg">
          <summary class="flex items-center justify-between p-4 cursor-pointer hover:bg-card/80">
            <h4 class="text-base text-white">Who is this coaching best suited for?</h4>
            <span class="text-accent group-open:rotate-180 transition-transform">+</span>
          </summary>
          <div class="p-4 pt-0 bg-gray-900/40 text-sm text-gray-300">
            This coaching is ideal for senior executives (C-suite, VPs, Directors, Senior Managers), Board Members, and Non-Executive Directors facing high-stakes negotiations, whether for a new role, appointment, promotion, or performance review. It's for leaders who want to strategically enhance their compensation and negotiation skills.
          </div>
        </details>
         <details class="group bg-card border border-gray-800 rounded-lg">
          <summary class="flex items-center justify-between p-4 cursor-pointer hover:bg-card/80">
            <h4 class="text-base text-white">What results can I expect?</h4>
            <span class="text-accent group-open:rotate-180 transition-transform">+</span>
          </summary>
          <div class="p-4 pt-0 bg-gray-900/40 text-sm text-gray-300">
            Clients typically gain increased confidence, a clear negotiation strategy, improved ability to articulate their value, and ultimately, secure better compensation packages (salary, bonus, terms). While specific outcomes vary, the goal is to maximize your negotiation success.
          </div>
        </details>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>

<style>
  @media (max-width: 640px) {
    .w-40 {
      max-width: 120px;
      height: auto;
    }
    .p-6 {
      padding: 1rem;
    }
    .text-xl {
      font-size: 1rem;
    }
    .text-2xl {
      font-size: 1.25rem;
    }
    .text-3xl {
      font-size: 1.5rem;
    }
    .text-4xl {
      font-size: 1.75rem;
    }
  }
</style>